title: Conversations: Seduction or Strategy? The Very Real Cleopatra VII with The Partial Historians
itunes:title: Conversations: Seduction or Strategy? The Very Real Cleopatra VII with The Partial Historians
itunes:subtitle: Dr. Rad and Dr. G of the Partial Historians Podcast give Liv a history lesson on Cleopatra VII.
description:
In a bit of a departure from other Conversations episodes, Dr. Rad and Dr. G of the Partial Historians Podcast give Liv a history lesson, with a rundown on the life of Cleopatra VII, the last Pharaoh of Egypt.

Subscribe to the Partial Historians podcast here.
